{"tid":2335383,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"當你遇到不講道理的共匪，你還需要講道理嗎？","createTime":"2020-12-22T00:12:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T07:10:31.000Z","uid":337052,"like":17,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bf68a41cccb2132ce4f84f398e6a0627f412b38a","tid":2335383,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T00:12:12.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">當你遇到不講道理的共匪，你還需要講道理嗎？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/12/22/218.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F12%2F22%2F218.jpg&h=68010d74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港終審法院廿一日裁定「緊急法」和「禁蒙面法」均合憲。圖為去年九月的「反送中」運動期間，示威者戴上面具、口罩與頭盔等蒙面物品，但今後無論合法或非法集會遊行，這些物品一律禁止。（法新社檔案照）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pJ6Ps6O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpJ6Ps6O.jpg&h=0b41e952&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n冬至平安"},{"pid":"d1be5e23cd8375c11d90e5c827673c0ff0db1d67","tid":2335383,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T00:13:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/12/22/217.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F12%2F22%2F217.jpg&h=b1211fd8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f3601f8bb06cd92046f259b92bdcf62c1cd77b68","tid":2335383,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T00:15:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://g.udn.com.tw/upfiles/B_WA/wang32488/PSN_PHOTO/209/f_12297209_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fg.udn.com.tw%2Fupfiles%2FB_WA%2Fwang32488%2FPSN_PHOTO%2F209%2Ff_12297209_1.jpg&h=3a4db357&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fc4ffbde8a9d51d5b8c588ed4f2a5a316aa5726e","tid":2335383,"uid":337052,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T00:16:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.hi-on.org.tw/Public/Image